00:40:57,270 --> 00:40:58,230
I should

1183
00:40:58,230 --> 00:41:00,630
give up control of the company?

1184
00:42:20,830 --> 00:42:21,400
Lin.

1185
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,440
Yiduo.

1186
00:42:22,750 --> 00:42:23,600
Why haven't you gone back yet?

1187
00:42:24,150 --> 00:42:24,560
I have a telephone meeting

1188
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:26,350
with a North America partner later.

1189
00:42:26,630 --> 00:42:27,440
It's so late.

1190
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,790
Why are you still here?

1191
00:42:29,830 --> 00:42:31,270
I'm catching up with the progress.

1192
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:32,310
I hope

1193
00:42:32,310 --> 00:42:33,310
our lab

1194
00:42:33,750 --> 00:42:35,270
