1195
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:37,630
You're so hasten to do it.

1196
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:40,040
The earlier it's done,

1197
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:41,120
the sooner

1198
00:42:41,120 --> 00:42:42,670
experimental results you can get.

1199
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:44,480
Then I can go home.

1200
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,670
Honestly, if I don't go back soon,

1201
00:42:46,670 --> 00:42:48,630
my family will forget me.

1202
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:51,120
You're exaggerating!

1203
00:42:51,630 --> 00:42:53,230
You're the breadwinner of your family.

1204
00:42:53,750 --> 00:42:55,350
I'm out there,

1205
00:42:55,350 --> 00:42:56,920
so, it is my wife who

1206
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:57,790
takes care of the family, right?

1207
00:43:02,400 --> 00:43:03,230
You've got something to say?

1208
00:43:04,750 --> 00:43:06,150
I've got good news to tell you.

1209
00:43:06,520 --> 00:43:06,960
Have a seat.

1210
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:07,670
Okay.

1211
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:16,350
A national-level

1212
00:43:16,350 --> 00:43:17,400
biological lab

1213
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:18,480
is

1214
00:43:18,600 --> 00:43:19,440
under preparation.

1215
00:43:19,750 --> 00:43:20,560
You're

1216
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:21,560
very fit

1217
00:43:21,560 --> 00:43:23,350
for the position of technical director.

1218
00:43:24,150 --> 00:43:25,270
I think

1219
00:43:25,270 --> 00:43:26,440
after our lab

1220
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,750
goes public,

1221
00:43:27,880 --> 00:43:29,230
I can recommend you to them.

1222
00:43:30,040 --> 00:43:31,230
Then you'll be in charge

1223
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:32,630
of lab projects.

1224
00:43:33,120 --> 00:43:33,960
You can become

1225
00:43:34,270 --> 00:43:35,270
a big shot

1226
00:43:35,270 --> 00:43:35,920
in the field.

1227
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:37,150
What do you think?

